ice officer]]. He returned from [[Israel]] on 26 February and several days later was admitted to the [[Dimitrie Gerota]] Emergency Hospital with flu-like symptoms, but lied about having travelled. Because of this, a penal case has been opened in his name.<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.digi24.ro/stiri/actualitate/justitie/coronavirus-pensionarul-de-la-mai-care-a-mintit-ca-nu-a-iesit-din-tara-are-dosar-penal-1273746 |title=Pensionarul de la MAI care a min\u021bit c\u0103 nu a ie\u0219it din \u021bar\u0103 are dosar penal |date=11 March 2020 |website=Digi24 |language=ro}}</ref> Israel's Minister of Tourism said he stayed in the Palestinian territories.<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.g4media.ro/ministerul-turismului-din-israel-pacientul-17-internat-la-spitalul-dimitrie-gerota-a-fost-cazat-in-teritoriile-palestiniene.html |title=Ministerul Turismului din Israel: \"Pacientul 17\", internat la spitalul Dimitrie Gerota, a fost cazat \u00een teritoriile palestiniene |date=12 March 2020 |website=G4Media}}</ref> [[Super-spreader]]; he infected at least 40 others.<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.digi24.ro/stiri/actualitate/pacientul-de-la-gerota-care-a-mintit-a-infectat-13-persoane-ultimele-patru-confirmate-vineri-tataru-arata-inconstienta-acelui-om-1274663 |title=Pacientul de la Gerota care a min\u021bit a infectat 13 persoane, ultimele patru confirmate vineri. T\u0103taru: \"Arat\u0103 incon\u0219tien\u021ba acelui om\" |date=13 March 2020 |website=Digi 24}}</ref>\n|-\n! 18\n| rowspan=\"12\" | 10 Mar.\n| {{Failure|Hospitalised}}\n| Local transmission\n| {{n/a}}\n| [[Ilfov County|Ilfov]]\n| Female\n| 31\n| Contact of case #12's girlfriend.\n| rowspan=\"8\" | <ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.hotnews.ro/stiri-sanatate-23712980-cazuri-coronavirus-confirmate-bucuresti-bilantul-covid19.htm |title=UPDATE \u00cenc\u0103 8 noi cazuri de coronavirus \u00een Bucure\u0219ti. Este cel mai mare num\u0103r confirmat \u00eentr-o singur\u0103 zi. Bilan\u021bul \u00eemboln\u0103virilor a aj